data.description: OPEN HOUSE - SATURDAY, 1/20 FROM 1-3 PM. REDUCED!!! HUGE LOT with endless possibilities! Room for additions, pool, truck, RV, boat, etc. NO HOA! NO Flood Insurance is required. Freshly painted! New Kitchen, Appliances, & Bathroom. Large Laundry/Pantry/Mudroom. As per the owner, 2019 New Roof, Termite Tented 2021, and new a/c. Huge 26X12 Permitted Hurricane Outside Building in the back yard, pictures do not show insulation that has been added to the outside building. Additionally, 2 other sheds, fruit trees, and sprinkler system which it runs on well water. EASY SHOWING!
